definitions.definition: A pipe or channel, or system of pipes or channels, used to remove human waste and to provide drainage .

main_definition: A pipe or channel, or system of pipes or channels, used to remove human waste and to provide drainage .

definitions.definition: ( historical ) An official in charge of a princely household , also responsible for the ceremonial task of attending at dinners, seating the guests and serving dishes.

main_definition: ( historical ) An official in charge of a princely household , also responsible for the ceremonial task of attending at dinners, seating the guests and serving dishes.

definitions.definition: A small tortricid moth , the larva of which sews together the edges of a leaf using silk .
